		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">兆载龙兽使用两翼各朝前施放一排的子弹，命中造成<span color="#bababa">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">兆载龙兽瞄准玩家，<span color="#ffcdbf">暴露腹部弱点</span><span>，使用两翼施放总共28个追踪弹，造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">80%,24%,8%,0.8%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="425" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">靠近兆载龙兽时，兆载龙兽使用头部进行挑击，左右各一次，每次造成<span color="#b9b9b9">60%</span><span>伤害，每次挑击时扔出3块石头，造成</span><span color="#bababa">80%,40%,16%</span><span>伤害，极大概率接扫尾。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">靠近兆载龙兽时，兆载龙兽原地旋转一圈，使用尾部齿轮造成<span color="#b9b9b9">75%</span><span>伤害，可能接翼坠。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="895" width="437" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">兆载龙兽<span color="#ffcebf">暴露头、胸部弱点</span><span>，使用核心朝地上发射大范围冲击，造成</span><span color="#bababa">100%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，空地巡状态皆可施放。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/重武装兆载永劫龙兽.assets/Image_24.png')" x="1248" y="822" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/重武装兆载永劫龙兽.assets/Image_25.png')" x="1248" y="598" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">兆载龙兽使用双翼分别朝地面砸去，均造成<span color="#b8b8b8">75%</span><span>伤害，每个翼落地后还将在外圈产生冲击波，造成</span><span color="#bababa">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1119" width="429" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">兆载龙兽<span color="#ffcebf">暴露头部弱点</span><span>，汲取</span><span textDecoration="underline">元素锚栓</span><span>的力量，向空中抛出20枚散弹，造成对应元素的</span><span color="#d8ffcc">100%,30%,10%</span><span>伤害，每个散弹有</span><span color="#ffcebf">33%</span><span>概率留下</span><span color="#bfdfff">元素氛</span><span>，之后转换空地巡状态，降落地面造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">30%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1319" y="1108" width="53" height="160" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" direction="rtl" blockProgression= "rl" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#bfdfff">元素氛<span color="#ffffff">如右<br/>对应元素的</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1374" width="998" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">施放「散落洪流」前，会立即吸收元素填充元素螺栓，使该次技能附上元素伤害，元素的种类以<span color="#ffebbf">上一周期</span><span>所受</span><span color="#ffbfbf">总和最高</span><span>的</span><span color="#ffeebf">伤害</span><span>为准</span><span color="#ffeebf">(物伤则无属性)</span><span>，</span><span color="#ffbfbf">不吸收附着的元素</span><span>。元素吸收完毕后该元素抗性</span><span color="#ffbfbf">+60%</span><span>，提升的抗性仅能通过吸收其他属性来转移。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/重武装兆载永劫龙兽.assets/Image_26.png')" x="720" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
