		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">靠近兆载龙兽时，兆载龙兽用尾部齿轮碾过，<span color="#ffcebf">暴露头部弱点</span><span>，造成</span><span color="#bababa">60%</span><span>伤害，若命中玩家则立即扫尾造成</span><span color="#bababa">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="421" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">兆载龙兽朝玩家冲来，<span color="#ffcebf">暴露头部弱点</span><span>，冲刺命中造成</span><span color="#bababa">75%</span><span>伤害，若命中玩家则立即扫尾造成</span><span color="#bababa">75%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#96673d" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#96673d">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1260" width="441" height="97" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">元素锚栓：吸收元素后，增加<span color="#ffbfbf">60%</span><span>该元素抗性。<br/>轻巡武装：升空后提供的护盾，2次特化次数盾，击破任意弱点-1次，耗尽后落地。<br/>重胄武装：升空后提供的护盾，不定次特化次数盾，击破双翼弱点需6次，击破头、胸弱点需3次，耗尽后落地。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
